[{"index": 0, "text": "How about maybe a little phrase or something, something in French that I could say?", "start": 0.0, "end": 3.121, "zh": "能不能教我一个短语之类的,一句法语我可以说说看?", "zh_hant": "能不能教我一個短語之類的,一句法語我可以說說看?"}, {"index": 1, "text": "Okay, I'll teach you something that I learned recently.", "start": 3.602, "end": 6.523, "zh": "好啊,我教你一个我最近学到的。", "zh_hant": "好啊,我教你一個我最近學到的。"}, {"index": 2, "text": "So they have, like, their slang is all inverting words.", "start": 7.084, "end": 11.185, "zh": "他们那种,俚语就是把词全部倒过来说。", "zh_hant": "他們那種,俚語就是把詞全部倒過來說。"}, {"index": 3, "text": "Oh.", "start": 11.686, "end": 12.286, "zh": "哦。", "zh_hant": "哦。"}, {"index": 4, "text": "And someone taught me once that, like, to know a language, you have to know how the pronunciation.", "start": 12.286, "end": 17.169, "zh": "有人曾经跟我说,要懂一门语言,你得懂它的发音。", "zh_hant": "有人曾經跟我說,要懂一門語言,你得懂它的發音。"}, {"index": 5, "text": "You have to know how they say, um, which for the French is, uh, uh.", "start": 17.169, "end": 20.55, "zh": "你得知道他们怎么说,呃,对法语来说就是,呃,呃。", "zh_hant": "你得知道他們怎麼說,呃,對法語來說就是,呃,呃。"}, {"index": 6, "text": "So, like, the whole, like, sound of the language is, uh.", "start": 21.811, "end": 24.432, "zh": "就是那种,整个语言的腔调是,呃。", "zh_hant": "就是那種,整個語言的腔調是,呃。"}, {"index": 7, "text": "You got to do it one more time.", "start": 24.432, "end": 25.673, "zh": "你得再来一遍。", "zh_hant": "你得再來一遍。"}, {"index": 8, "text": "Uh.", "start": 27.054, "end": 27.634, "zh": "呃。", "zh_hant": "呃。"}, {"index": 9, "text": "like with their thing.", "start": 27.934, "end": 29.154, "zh": "就像带着他们那种感觉。", "zh_hant": "就像帶著他們那種感覺。"}, {"index": 10, "text": "So, okay, this phrase is, c 'est trop chelou.", "start": 29.955, "end": 32.836, "zh": "好,这句话是,c'est trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "好,這句話是,c'est trop chelou。"}, {"index": 11, "text": "Oh, c 'est trop.", "start": 32.836, "end": 35.178, "zh": "哦,c'est trop。", "zh_hant": "哦,c'est trop。"}, {"index": 12, "text": "C 'est trop.", "start": 35.178, "end": 35.968, "zh": "C'est trop。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop。"}, {"index": 13, "text": "C 'est trop.", "start": 35.968, "end": 36.598, "zh": "C'est trop。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop。"}, {"index": 14, "text": "Chelou.", "start": 36.598, "end": 37.319, "zh": "Chelou。", "zh_hant": "Chelou。"}, {"index": 15, "text": "Chelou.", "start": 37.479, "end": 38.069, "zh": "Chelou。", "zh_hant": "Chelou。"}, {"index": 16, "text": "Trop chelou.", "start": 38.069, "end": 38.789, "zh": "Trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "Trop chelou。"}, {"index": 17, "text": "C 'est trop chelou.", "start": 38.789, "end": 39.61, "zh": "C'est trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop chelou。"}, {"index": 18, "text": "Exactly.", "start": 39.61, "end": 41.484, "zh": "没错。", "zh_hant": "沒錯。"}, {"index": 19, "text": "It means too shady.", "start": 41.484, "end": 42.266, "zh": "意思是太可疑了。", "zh_hant": "意思是太可疑了。"}, {"index": 20, "text": "Shady.", "start": 42.416, "end": 42.526, "zh": "可疑。", "zh_hant": "可疑。"}, {"index": 21, "text": "It's shady.", "start": 42.526, "end": 44.69, "zh": "这很可疑。", "zh_hant": "這很可疑。"}, {"index": 22, "text": "C 'est trop chelou.", "start": 44.912, "end": 46.114, "zh": "C'est trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop chelou。"}, {"index": 23, "text": "C 'est trop chelou.", "start": 46.114, "end": 47.055, "zh": "C'est trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop chelou。"}, {"index": 24, "text": "C 'est trop chelou.", "start": 47.055, "end": 47.827, "zh": "C'est trop chelou。", "zh_hant": "C'est trop chelou。"}, {"index": 25, "text": "Euh.", "start": 47.827, "end": 48.058, "zh": "呃。", "zh_hant": "呃。"}]